      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my reliable ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! It\u2019s been well-loved and is in great shape for its next adventure. Everything runs smoothly, and it's perfect for daily commutes or weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin\u2014you're going to love how it handles!",
