    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available for the discerning driver: a BMW E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS variable valve timing. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 420G 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis has been enhanced with rear subframe reinforcement and a refreshed suspension featuring Bilstein dampers for precise lateral dynamics. Mechanically robust, it delivers a linear power band up to an 8,000 RPM redline, offering a pure analog connection to the road. Recent service includes a valve adjustment and cooling system overhaul.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
